Directory for PowerShell Scripts

Yes, now i have computer with windows 7 on it and i can write some scripts on this shell :-)

###### ABOUT SCRIPTS ######
diff.ps1 - Script for making diff's beetwin 2 files
Search-Help.ps1 - Script for searching help in Powershell Documentation by keyword or reg-exp

###### TIP'S & TRIC'S ######
Вызов PowerShell из любого командгого файла - PowerShell "& 'полный путь до скрипта.ps1' аргументы"